  "pc0_js1" -> "pc2_js1" [label="υ ∧ ¬ω ∨ ¬τ ∧ ¬υ ∧ level(c0) ⊐ pc ∨ ¬τ ∧ ¬υ ∧ level(c0) ⊑ pc,\n\
